abstract: >
  Cumulative public checkpoint for Deep Origin Theory. It preserves the J2C
  structural action-class public pre-execution lock and restores the standalone
  Help Us Verify English and Arabic companion packages as sibling public files.
  The release contains no known J2C result, no J2C galaxy fit, no
  data-selected cosmological background, and no final cosmic-closure claim.
